(note: these are custom keybindings!)

```
^   = Ctrl
M - = Alt (or meta key)
```

## NANO

```
^H      : Toggle help
M-H     : Toggle help mode
^C      : Cursor position data 
M-M     : Toggle mouse mode
M-Shift-3 : Toggle line numbers
M-D     : Doc statistics
M-Y     : Toggle syntax highlighting
```

## FILE HANDLING

```
^O     : Open / new file
^W     : Save buffer as...
^S     : Save buffer
^Q     : Close buffer & exit
```

## MOVE

```
▶     : One char forward
◀     : One char backward
^▶    : One word forward
^◀    : One word backward
▲      : Goto previous line
▼      : Goto next line
^▲     : Goto previous textblock
^▼     : Goto next textblock
^T     : Goto line
M-(    : Goto paragraph start
M-)    : Goto paragraph end
```

## SEARCH & REPLACE

```
^F     : Search forward
^G     : Search next occurrence
^B     : Search backward
^D     : Search last occurrence
^R     : Replace
^]     : Find matching bracket
```

## EDIT

```
^A     : Mark text from cursor
Shift+Arrows : Mark text
^C     : Copy line / text
^X     : Cut line / text
^P     : Paste line
^U     : Undo
^E     : Redo
^J     : Justify current paragraph
^Y     : Involve spell checker
^Del   : Del from crsr 2 word end
Shft^Del : Del from crsr 2 word start
```
